channel.title: Need some help With java please?
channel.description:
Hi, I downloaded Java 6u1 to my pc and i downloaded: jdk-6u1-windows-i586-p.exe AND jdk-6u1-windows-i586-p-iftw.exe
My compiler detected I had Java but it kept saying all sorts of crap and wouldnt let me run my server. I asked around and was told to download the latest JDK? I am using Mod tahrocks perfect compiler.
WHAT DO I DOWNLOAD? The 2 i downloaded? just 1 of them? Or am I not even supposed to be downloading Java 6u1? Please Help?![br][size=1]Posted on: June 14, 2007, 09:46:00 AM[/size][hr]
Oh and if there is any nice people out there who could add me on msn and give some advice from time to time about things I would be very grateful
